The paper focuses on machine learning interpretability and its application in designing decision support systems for clinicians. Therefore, cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also discusses the importance of building trust in ML models, which falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ML in medicine, which could fall under the sub-categories of Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science (cs.CE).
